Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狡嚙先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你別動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槙島可就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人我也不會放過
